You know, all I hear nowadays is how Bush has done this wrong and that wrong.<br>
<br>
If you don't like it, don't just bitch about it.  Come up with a new productive point of view. Present this idea to the public.  And then let it take form from there.. none of us have all the answers but when ideas are tossed around, amazing new ideas can be formed.<br>
<br>
Just sick of all the negative bullshit in the media and politics these days.<br>
<br>
For the love of god, why are there so many people who always seem to think they know what is wrong, yet have no good ideas on how to make it better.<br>
<br>
If you can't fix it, don't piss on it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=andvarishadowmist>AndvariShadowmist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bastard Bard</span><br>  Posts: 2862<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(9/22/03 6:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3549.topic&index=86>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sick of this political bullshit</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>And only published in non english speaking news agency media. =P <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
